## DESIGN DECISIONS

### Phase 3 Architectural Choices:

1. **License Manager**:
- HMAC-SHA256 for signature (tamper-resistant)
- Device binding using fingerprint (security)
- Encrypted storage for license data
- Future-proof schema (ready for server activation)
- License key format: VM-PRO-XXXXXXXXXXXX (20 random chars)
- Constant-time comparison (prevents timing attacks)

2. **Feature Flags**:
- Centralized gating (single source of truth)
- Simple boolean checks throughout app
- Tier-based categorization (Free/Pro/Enterprise future)
- Easy to add new features
- Upgrade benefits clearly defined
- Convenience functions for common checks

3. **Integration**:
- License manager uses storage manager (encryption)
- License manager uses device fingerprint (binding)
- Feature flags use is_pro() result (simple)
- Detection engine checks is_pro for Pro patterns
- Session manager will check limits via feature flags
- All components modular and testable

4. **Security**:
- HMAC prevents signature forging
- Device binding prevents license sharing
- Encrypted storage protects license data
- Constant-time comparison prevents timing attacks
- Tamper detection (device + signature changes)

